        <content type="html">
            <![CDATA[
                    <img src="http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/publii.png" alt="" />
                <p>There are three sizes of cactuses. Depending on which one you click you get 1, 2 or 3 points. Pressing reset restarts the count at zero.</p>
<p>The phone screams when you touch a cactus. Phones can’t deliver an electric shock yet, else that would have been an option. ;-)</p>
<p>You are allowed to use the sounds and images.</p>
<p>All images are from <a href="http://www.pixabay.com/">www.pixabay.com</a> and are in the public domain.</p>
